#: ../../source/manage/configure-health-check-probes.rst:7
msgid ""
"This page describes how to configure health check probes for a Mattermost"
" server."
msgstr "이 페이지는 Mattermost 서버의 상태 확인 프로브를 구성하는 방법을 설명합니다."

#: ../../source/manage/configure-health-check-probes.rst:9
msgid ""
"Before you begin, you should have a running Mattermost server. If you "
"don't, you can :doc:`install Mattermost on various distributions </guides"
"/deployment-guide>`."
msgstr "시작하기 전에 실행 중인 Mattermost 서버가 있어야 합니다. 없다면 :doc:`다양한 배포판에 Mattermost 설치 </guides/deployment-guide>` 할 수 있습니다."

#: ../../source/manage/configure-health-check-probes.rst:13
msgid ""
":doc:`Highly available Mattermost cluster support </scale/high-"
"availability-cluster-based-deployment>` requires Mattermost Enterprise."
msgstr ":doc:`고가용성 Mattermost 클러스터 지원 </scale/high-availability-cluster-based-deployment>` 은 Mattermost Enterprise가 필요합니다."

#: ../../source/manage/configure-health-check-probes.rst:15
msgid "You can perform a health check with the following 2 methods:"
msgstr "다음 2가지 방법으로 상태 확인을 수행할 수 있습니다:"

#: ../../source/manage/configure-health-check-probes.rst:17
msgid "`ping the APIv4 endpoint <#ping-the-apiv4-endpoint>`__"
msgstr "`APIv4 엔드포인트 핑 <#ping-the-apiv4-endpoint>`__"

#: ../../source/manage/configure-health-check-probes.rst:18
msgid "`ping the Mattermost server <#ping-the-mattermost-server>`__"
msgstr "`Mattermost 서버 핑 <#ping-the-mattermost-server>`__"

#: ../../source/manage/configure-health-check-probes.rst:21
msgid "Ping the APIv4 endpoint"
msgstr "APIv4 엔드포인트 핑"

#: ../../source/manage/configure-health-check-probes.rst:23
#, python-format
msgid ""
"You can use the `GET /system/ping APIv4 endpoint "
"<https://api.mattermost.com/#tag/system%2Fpaths%2F~1system~1ping%2Fget>`_"
" to check for system health."
msgstr "시스템 상태를 확인하기 위해 `GET /system/ping APIv4 엔드포인트 <https://api.mattermost.com/#tag/system%2Fpaths%2F~1system~1ping%2Fget>`_ 를 사용할 수 있습니다."

#: ../../source/manage/configure-health-check-probes.rst:25
msgid ""
"A sample request is included below. The endpoint checks if the server is "
"up and healthy based on the configuration setting "
"``GoRoutineHealthThreshold``."
msgstr "아래에 샘플 요청이 포함되어 있습니다. 엔드포인트는 ``GoRoutineHealthThreshold`` 설정을 기반으로 서버가 정상 작동하고 있는지 확인합니다."

#: ../../source/manage/configure-health-check-probes.rst:27
msgid ""
"If ``GoRoutineHealthThreshold`` and the number of goroutines on the "
"server exceeds that threshold, the server is considered unhealthy."
msgstr "``GoRoutineHealthThreshold`` 와 서버의 고루틴 수가 해당 임계값을 초과하면 서버는 비정상으로 간주됩니다."

#: ../../source/manage/configure-health-check-probes.rst:28
msgid ""
"If ``GoRoutineHealthThreshold`` is not set or the number of goroutines is"
" below the threshold the server is considered healthy."
msgstr "``GoRoutineHealthThreshold`` 가 설정되지 않았거나 고루틴 수가 임계값 미만이면 서버는 정상으로 간주됩니다."

#: ../../source/manage/configure-health-check-probes.rst:30
msgid ""
"This endpoint can also be provided to schedulers like `Kubernetes "
"<https://kubernetes.io/docs/tasks/configure-pod-container/configure-"
"liveness-readiness-startup-probes/>`_."
msgstr "이 엔드포인트는 `Kubernetes <https://kubernetes.io/docs/tasks/configure-pod-container/configure-liveness-readiness-startup-probes/>`_ 와 같은 스케줄러에도 제공될 수 있습니다."

#: ../../source/manage/configure-health-check-probes.rst:43
msgid "Ping the Mattermost server"
msgstr "Mattermost 서버 핑"

#: ../../source/manage/configure-health-check-probes.rst:45
msgid ""
"The `Mattermost Probe <https://github.com/csduarte/mattermost-probe>`_ "
"constantly pings a Mattermost server using a variety of probes."
msgstr "`Mattermost Probe <https://github.com/csduarte/mattermost-probe>`_ 는 다양한 프로브를 사용하여 Mattermost 서버를 지속적으로 핑합니다."

#: ../../source/manage/configure-health-check-probes.rst:47
msgid ""
"These probes can be configured to verify core features, including sending"
" and receiving messages, joining channels, pinging a login page, and "
"searching of users and channels."
msgstr "이러한 프로브는 메시지 송수신, 채널 참여, 로그인 페이지 핑, 사용자 및 채널 검색을 포함한 핵심 기능을 확인하도록 구성할 수 있습니다."

